{"type": "article", "id": 17590, "title": "果汁包装系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-16T07:10:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104227xlaD4eSnTjUrtPyc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是日本时尚设计师藤原浩为纽约餐厅 The Butcher’s Daughter 设计的果汁包装，有橙汁和可可汁两种，分别以橙色和棕色为主。都采用方形色块拼接的方式，让颜色跳跃却统一，非常轻快活泼。色块上面有白色的闪电 logo 和手写文字，很生活。包装的其余部分都用了纯白色，简约大气。另有配套的 T 恤和购物袋。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144632tfbJUsqhHGSV9ZeW.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144632vhwTuSjDQqfU8WmA.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144633UhvnBcbPJgNo9w2C.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144634E8UGKLDzmgBbyXj1.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144635bFMXmqRnZ7VpaiOf.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}